---
title: "US19 — Workout reminders"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Registered Free User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>NotificationsScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>ManageNotificationPrefs / ScheduleReminder
  participant E as «Entity»<br/>Profile (notification_prefs)
  A->>B: toggle "Daily reminder" on
  B->>C: setEnabled(workout_reminder, true)
  C->>E: updateNotificationPrefs(userId, prefs)
  E-->>C: saved
  C->>E: scheduleReminder(workout_reminder, time)
  E-->>C: scheduled
  C-->>B: state = AsyncData (prefs)
  B-->>A: reminder fires at preferred time (rule-based, not AI)
  note over E: prefs via ProfileGateway → profiles (RLS) [BUILT] -<br/>scheduleReminder via NotificationGateway (flutter_local_notifications) [planned] - rule-based, no AI
